metadata.name: Buscando a Bolívar - Venezuela#09
metadata.description:
Trans-Andean Highway in Mérida. Venezuela 2013.

"Buscando a Bolívar" is the result of my journeys through Bolivia, Ecuador and Venezuela between 2009 and 2014, during the presidencies of Evo Morales, Rafael Correa and Hugo Chavez. 
Along this route I found much more than I was looking for. I was dazzled by the unexpected, actracted by the ambiguity and the complexity; which are the very essence of reality.
